Upsets...who picked 'em -- 

Oh Harvard Crimson, why did you pick this year to win your first NCAA game ever? My own bracket, which I'd now burn if it wasn't electronic, had New Mexico all the way to the final game. Oh well, I will live vicariously through Carson (#1! #1!), who was amongst the 41 that nailed this pick.

