Shout Outs 
where I pseudo-randomly (by which I mean not randomly at all) give a shout out to one or many of you, my loyal pool contestants.

I'm going to open this section with a first in JQMCBP email shout out history: I'm going to shout out to a specific filter in the JQMCBP Filtermatic(TM) (http://benklaas.com/jqmcbp/filtermatic.cgi). For those new to this exciting* tool, you can create filters so you can view the leaderboard with just a subset of players. Typically this is done so people that know each other can have a little on-the-side competition away from The Quest for Candy(TM). But this filter, 'The Nicknames List', authored by persons unknown, attempts to get together everyone that entered some kind of nickname for themselves. It's an amusing list, currently with 'Never too fresh' Soren Van Houten beating the other nomes de plume**.

http://benklaas.com/jqmcbp/leaderboard.cgi?view=All&sort=rank&order=asc&filter=1354&man_or_chimp=man

* generally not that exciting
** yeah, that's right. nomes de plume.

