Candy Bar of the Day --
where I single out one or two of my favorite candy selections

As I've done since his brackets became available publicly a few years ago, I've entered President Barack Obama's bracket in the pool (he is currently tied for 528th place). His candy selection of "The One Usher Stole from Me" has some delicious backstory.

http://newsroom.mtv.com/2009/01/19/usher-recalls-stealing-barack-obamas-candy-bar/

 "We had been campaigning all day, all over the place, and I kind of look around and I'm like, 'Oooh, let me eat this candy bar or whatever,' " Usher remembered. "And we both look at it, and I'm like, 'You're not gonna eat that, are you?' and he's like, 'You're not gonna eat it, are you?' I'm like, 'Well, I'm gonna eat it if you don't.' "


And I'm like, 'Usher, why are you like talking like you are a teenager?' and he's like 'Shut up I'm Usher'

